{"tid":37920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯新規定將啤酒歸為酒精飲品","createTime":"2016-12-13T15:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T23:33:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a646295befb5a2165fd6a8f12e0d5ff4365bea","tid":37920,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"周二開始生效的新規則使俄羅斯人更難購買啤酒。在這之前，啤酒被歸入食品，因為啤酒含酒精低於10%。<br />\n<br />\n現在啤酒被歸入酒精飲料，這就意味著街頭售貨亭和街角商店不能出售啤酒。<br />\n<br />\n該措施是俄羅斯努力減少酗酒努力的一部分，酗酒每年導致50萬俄羅斯人死亡。"},{"pid":"9880628052746c5ddfd8ab9f0871092c9bf8c495","tid":37920,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:14:45.000Z","msg":".....，原來之前唔係"},{"pid":"947d888a245652cfc97c4aa9c829c641128fcce7","tid":37920,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>.....，原來之前唔係</blockquote><br />\n一直在玩命"},{"pid":"b1ef92bf460c6a995e4e0fa723dae9d8bb28b544","tid":37920,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c63f0b883a2f5e78e1b1aa77bc291f407cad34e","tid":37920,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>.....，原來之前唔係</blockquote><br />\n一直在玩命</blockquote><br />\n人哋本來當汽水咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730cafda2232f94ab44afaa5e6f77c3c7f03b04a","tid":37920,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730e0299ce98e38199732247ecda3b8ad5d7bf18","tid":37920,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5c300ba14db37f66a0e462ce04606ef59fd04f","tid":37920,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"2013年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯新規定將啤酒歸入酒精飲料<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<br />\n2013年1月1日 16:43<br />\n周二開始生效的新規則使俄羅斯人更難購買啤酒。在這之前，啤酒被歸入食品，因為啤酒含酒精低於10%。<br />\n<br />\n現在啤酒被歸入酒精飲料，這就意味著街頭售貨亭和街角商店不能出售啤酒。<br />\n<br />\n該措施是俄羅斯努力減少酗酒努力的一部分，酗酒每年導致50萬俄羅斯人死亡。"},{"pid":"6a9c1ecb03afbdb165df05925d8c543f13992fb3","tid":37920,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976c7d75810667cab0284a7d8a4e46d4cb0e9301","tid":37920,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:33:23.000Z","msg":"2013...."}]}